<pb ed="T" id="T20.1178.0778a" n="0778a"/>
<lb n="0778a01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0778a02"/><head type="no">No. 1178</head>
<lb n="0778a03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0778001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】三十帖策子第二十六，【甲】黃檗版淨嚴等校訂加筆本</note>文殊<note n="0778002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔菩薩〕－【甲】</note><app n="0778002"><lem>菩薩</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>獻佛陀羅尼名<note n="0778003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">烏＝鳥【甲】</note><app n="0778003"><lem>烏</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">鳥</rdg></app>蘇
<lb n="0778a04"/>吒<note place="inline">此云滅婬<note n="0778004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">慾＝欲【甲】＊</note><app n="0778004"><lem>慾</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">欲</rdg></app>&CB00230;我慢</note></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0778a05"/>
<lb n="0778a06"/><div1 type="jing"><p>時佛&CB00330;阿難。為未來沒苦眾生。廣宣流布。時
<lb n="0778a07"/>文殊菩薩先說偈言</p>
<lb n="0778a08"/><lg><l>一切眾生類</l><l>迴<note n="0778005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">沒＝波【甲】</note><app n="0778005"><lem>沒</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">波</rdg></app>婬鬼界</l>
<lb n="0778a09"/><l>無能覺之者</l><l><note n="0778006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯＝惟【甲】</note><app n="0778006"><lem>唯</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">惟</rdg></app>我能救拔</l>
<lb n="0778a10"/><l>永斷生死本</l><l>普處寂滅樂</l></lg>
<lb n="0778a11"/><p>即說陀羅尼曰</p>
<lb n="0778a12"/><p type="dharani">句利句利帝那憂<note n="0778007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拙＝杜【甲】＊</note><app n="0778007"><lem>拙</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">杜</rdg></app>憂<app type="＊" source="0778007"><lem>拙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">杜</rdg></app>帝那度呼度呼帝
<lb n="0778a13"/>那究吒究吒帝那若<note n="0778008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蜜＝密【甲】下同</note><app n="0778008"><lem>蜜</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">密</rdg></app>都若蜜都帝那究吒
<lb n="0778a14"/>呼究吒呼帝那憂守憂守帝那耶蜜若耶蜜若
<lb n="0778a15"/>帝那度呼吒究吒多薩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二<note n="0778009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＋（引）【甲】</note><app n="0778009"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">合引</rdg></app></note><note n="0778010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訶＋（引）細註【甲】</note><app n="0778010"><lem>訶</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">訶<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0778a16"/><p>右誦&CB00057;三遍。結縷作七結繫&CB00560;。是&CB00057;能令諸
<lb n="0778a17"/>失心者。還得正念。滅婬<app type="＊" source="0778004"><lem>慾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">欲</rdg></app>火除我慢結。三
<lb n="0778a18"/>毒垢盡自然清<note n="0778011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">涼＝淨【甲】</note><app n="0778011"><lem>涼</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">淨</rdg></app>。若有精神。<note n="0778012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">沈＝沒【甲】</note><app n="0778012"><lem>沈</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">沒</rdg></app>在無明重
<lb n="0778a19"/>淵之下。久溺生死不得出要。<note n="0778013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嗚＝鳴【甲】</note><app n="0778013"><lem>嗚</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">鳴</rdg></app>呼深可傷。
<lb n="0778a20"/>若人心得<note n="0778014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">醒＝惺【甲】</note><app n="0778014"><lem>醒</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">惺</rdg></app>悟極自厭污。此是凡夫愚下鬼
<lb n="0778a21"/>神畜生之所行處。非梵行所宜。非聖人所願。
<lb n="0778a22"/>如此之人方可<note n="0778015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受＝授【甲】</note><app n="0778015"><lem>受</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">授</rdg></app>與此陀羅尼。勿傳矯俗疑
<lb n="0778a23"/><note n="0778016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">謗＝豫【甲】</note><app n="0778016"><lem>謗</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">豫</rdg></app>少信。縱持無<note n="0778017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">驗＝福【甲】</note><app n="0778017"><lem>驗</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">福</rdg></app>即轉退墮。若至誠誦者
<lb n="0778a24"/><note n="0778018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（婬）＋慾【甲】</note><app n="0778018"><lem>慾</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">婬慾</rdg></app>火漸<note n="0778019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盡＝消滅婬欲滅已慢心自滅慢心滅已其心則定其心定心結使都滅【甲】</note><app n="0778019"><lem>盡</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">消滅婬欲滅已慢心自滅慢心滅已其心則定其心定心結使都滅</rdg></app>。結使滅已心得解脫。心解脫已
<lb n="0778a25"/><note n="0778020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">則＝即【甲】</note><app n="0778020"><lem>則</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">即</rdg></app>得道果。是則神力功用誠諦不虛。行此
<lb n="0778a26"/>法者斷<note n="0778021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">酒＋（肉）【甲】</note><app n="0778021"><lem>酒</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">酒肉</rdg></app>五辛血食。男子<note n="0778022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔唯用〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0778022"><lem>唯用</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>九九八十
<lb n="0778a27"/>一日。女子<app type="＊" source="0778022"><lem>唯用</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>七七四十九日。晝夜六時勤
<lb n="0778a28"/>心讀誦。燒沈水白檀香散花。供養十方諸佛。
<lb n="0778a29"/>晝三夜三慎勿廢忘。日數未滿餘時之中。獨
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1178.0778b" n="0778b"/>
<lb n="0778b01"/>處山窟精舍。若聚落<note n="0778023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">即淨室三字甲本作夾註</note><note n="0778023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（即淨室）三字本文＝（即淨室）三字夾註【甲】</note><app n="0778023"><lem><note place="inline">即淨室</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">即淨室</note></rdg></app>四向遠人。當深生
<lb n="0778b02"/>欣躍自發慶幸。今我遭遇大聖神力。此身宜
<lb n="0778b03"/>至佛身。不懼淪溺。如是淨心念念信向。斷諸
<lb n="0778b04"/>惡作轉雜言論離間之語。不念名利。如是日
<lb n="0778b05"/>數足已。決定解脫其心泰然無復<note n="0778024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">欲＝慾【甲】</note><app n="0778024"><lem>欲</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">慾</rdg></app><note n="0778025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">慢字次行甲本有文殊滅婬我慢陀羅尼十字</note>慢</p><juan fun="close" n="001"></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>